# Class: <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Magazine> (Magazine)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Magazine> "A periodical of magazine Articles. A magazine is a publication that is issued periodically, usually bound in a paper cover, and typically contains essays, stories, poems, etc., by many writers, and often photographs and drawings, frequently specializing in a particular subject or area, as hobbies, news, or sports."@en)
