# Class: <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Series> (Series)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Series> "A loose, thematic, collection of Documents, often Books."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:isDefinedBy <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Series> "http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/"^^xsd:anyURI)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Series> "Series"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2003/06/sw-vocab-status/ns#term_status> <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Series> "stable")
SubClassOf(<http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Series> <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Collection>)
SubClassOf(<http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Series> ObjectAllValuesFrom(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/hasPart> <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Document>))

# Class: <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Slide> (Slide)

