AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/status/peerReviewed> "The process by which articles are chosen to be included in a refereed journal. An editorial board consisting of experts in the same field as the author review the article and decide if it is authoritative enough for publication."@en)
